With: Ingela Olsson, Johan Hallstr√∂m, Melinda Kinnaman
Synopsis:
Stella visits her invalid mother on an island in the Swedish archipelago, in an attempt to reconnect after years of estrangement. She brings with her a box of crumbled stone which awakens memories in them both.

But Stella and her mother remember things very differently.